      "rdf:value": "<L>18526<pc>107,1<k1>avAcya<k2>avAcya<h>2<e>2\r\n<hom>2.</hom> <s>avAcya</s> ¦ <lex>mfn.</lex> southern, southerly, <ls>L.</ls><info lex=\"m:f:n\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
