      "csl:lineNumber": 44744,
      "csl:pageColumn": "0193-a",
      "rdf:value": "<L>4953<pc>0193-a<k1>avAcya<k2>avAcya\n{#avAcya#}¦ {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@1@} Not proper to be <lbinfo n=\"ad+dressed\"/>\naddressed; {#avAcyo dIkzito nAmnA#} <lbinfo n=\"yavI#yAnapi\"/>\n{#yavIyAnapi yo Bavet#} <ls>Ms. 2. 128.</ls> {@--2@} <lbinfo n=\"Impro+per\"/>\nImproper to be uttered; vile, bad; {#avAcyaM#}\n{#vadato jihvA kaTaM na patitA tava#} <ls>Rām.</ls>;\n{#˚vAdAMSca bahUn vadizyaMti tavAhitAH#}  <lbinfo n=\"ls:Bg. 2.+ 36.\"/>\n<ls>Bg. 2. 36.</ls> {@--3@} Not distinctly expressed, not\nexpressible in words; {#˚tA, ˚tvaM#} <lbinfo n=\"impro+priety\"/>\nimpropriety; reproach, calumny. {@--Comp.@}\n{#--deSaH#} ‘the unspeakable place,’ the\nvulva ({#yoni#}).\n<LEND>"
    },
